                <note rend="inline" type="source">715.1715/430: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Honduras</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Lay</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-02-19T17:00:00-05:00"
                            >February 19, 1931—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>13. The following telegram to Managua is repeated for your information and for
                    action by you in accordance with paragraph 3. Please report results.</p>
                <p>[Here follows text of telegram No. 19, February 19, 5 p.m. to the Minister in
                    Nicaragua, printed <hi rend="italic">supra.</hi>]</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
